 & =y_{t}y_{t}^{\prime}-y_{t}(A_{1}y_{t-1}+\ldots+A_{p}y_{t-p})^{\prime}-(A_{1}y_{t-1}+\ldots+A_{p}y_{t-p})y_{t}^{\prime}+(A_{1}y_{t-1}+\ldots+A_{p}y_{t-p})(A_{1}y_{t-1}+\ldots+A_{p}y_{t-p})^{\prime}\\
